# Group the data by shape, quad, and year
grouped_data <- LEAVES_3040
group_by(grouped_data, Shape, Quad, Year)
# Calculate the mean and standard deviation for the Length variable for each group
summary_data <- grouped_data
summarize(summary_data, mean = mean(Length),
            sd = sd(Length))
